### 1. @RequestParam - query string 각각 받기
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus?keyword=coffe&categoryCode=2&page=1

### 2. @RequestParam - query string 전체 받기
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/search?keyword=coffe&categoryCode=2&page=1

### 3. @PathVariable - URL 경로 값 받기
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/5

### 4. @RequestBody - JSON 요청 본문을 DTO로 받기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus
Content-Type: application/json    //요청 보내는 Type 명시 필요
//MenuDTO 변수와 동일해야함
//헤더와 JSON 바디 사이는 반드시 '한 줄' 띄우기!

{
    "name" : "아이스 아메리카노",
    "price" : 5000,
    "categoryCode" : 2,
    "orderableStatus": "Y"
}

### 5. @RequestBody - 요청 본문을 문자열로 그대로 받기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/raw
Content-Type: text/plain

plain text

### 6. @RequestHeader, @CookieValue
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/request-info
User-Agent: IntelliJ HTTP Client(sent reqeust by IntelliJ test tool)
cookie: JSESSIONID=test-session-id

### 7. HTTPSession - session에 값 저장
POST localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/session?id=user01

### 8. HttpSession - session 값 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/session

### 9. HttpSession - session 만료
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/menus/session
